# Environment Variables

## Required for Production

```bash
# OpenWeather API Key (optional - has fallbacks)
OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweather_api_key_here

# Agmarknet Server URL (optional - defaults to localhost:5000)
AGMARKNET_API_URL=http://your-agmarknet-server:5000

# Database Configuration (optional - uses in-memory by default)
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/agritech

# Logging Level
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
```

## Optional Configuration

```bash
# Redis for caching (optional)
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# Sentry for error tracking (optional)
SENTRY_DSN=your_sentry_dsn_here

# API Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_PER_MINUTE=60
```

## Development Setup

For development, you can run without any environment variables - the system will use intelligent defaults and fallbacks.
